Package: excel2r
Title: Migrate Excel Workbooks to R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Eirini", "Mantzouni", email = "emantzo@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Converts Excel formula workbooks into standalone R scripts.
    Extracts every formula, translates 62 Excel functions to R equivalents,
    resolves cross-sheet references, determines execution order via topological
    sort, detects named tables, and optionally exports raw data as tidy CSVs
    for a fully Excel-free workflow. Includes built-in verification comparing
    R-computed values against Excel's cached results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
